Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.49,0:00:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.69,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.16,0:00:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.70,0:00:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.81,0:00:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.02,0:00:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.82,0:00:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.10,0:01:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.54,0:01:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.21,0:01:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.85,0:01:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十一話\N[悲傷的卡特爾]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.20,0:02:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!那裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是聯合的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.19,0:02:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看來醒來了呢，身體還好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.86,0:02:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是採掘資源用的衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.06,0:02:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何會在那種機動戰士裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.30,0:02:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外表看來又不是聯合的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.77,0:02:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.94,0:02:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還不可以動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那樣繼續漂流下去就會死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.88,0:02:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳為何…要救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.81,0:02:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是醫生，和OZ及聯合無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.72,0:02:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而這裡是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.02,0:02:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不屬於任何一方的中立地帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，妳救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還未向妳道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.03,0:03:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳知道能借\N穿梭機的地方嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.03,0:03:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊，身體這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.80,0:03:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可以讓病人離去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎樣也不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你急於做甚麼都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.77,0:03:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那對你的身體無益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.81,0:03:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在最重要是讓身心休息啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能準備穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能等嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.15,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能…我不自量力，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小事一樁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，你要休養到那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一言為定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，目標繼續加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里歐部隊會被拋離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.58,0:03:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍然向B區前進，沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.01,0:04:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙用里歐畢竟追不上嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.72,0:04:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有報告確認到那是托爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.59,0:04:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是甚麼都好，我們不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.06,0:04:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓拿著武器的機動戰士接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.46,0:04:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出動MD就能馬上解決它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.16,0:04:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些技師有聯絡來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.17,0:04:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型機動戰士完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜葉特和麥丘留士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想測試它們的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!能馬上投入實戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰出任另一個駕駛員?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳讓我出戰，蕾蒂‧安特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了記錄完整的數據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.82,0:04:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是技術相當的駕駛員會礙手礙腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.32,0:04:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.52,0:04:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我交由你指揮消滅托爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.02,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳覺得拜葉特和麥丘留士如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.52,0:05:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.82,0:05:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不愧曾設計過鋼彈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.76,0:05:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小意思\N對我們來說易如反掌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.16,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是讓那個鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛麥丘留士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才要他駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.11,0:05:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙身為駕駛員的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ應該最清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麥丘留士的自爆裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.74,0:05:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在特洛瓦的拜葉特裡控制吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.05,0:05:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，我已經照妳的吩咐弄妥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦\N如果他有任何可疑舉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以引爆麥丘留士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那必要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他以前在西伯利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.53,0:05:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾和托爾吉斯戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.46,0:05:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他只會想著決一勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次衛星不會被用作擋箭牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.97,0:06:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令戰鬥中斷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何知道那件事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.61,0:06:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那點事，OZ的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.97,0:06:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,查一下馬上就會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.44,0:06:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好他自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.38,0:06:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身在衛星的我或許已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.28,0:06:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要感謝他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為全靠他，我才能得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.59,0:06:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦你這個優秀部下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.25,0:06:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.75,0:06:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯，操縱性和\N鋼彈幾乎沒分別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會怎樣和MD戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.37,0:07:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先潛入敵人之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.24,0:07:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把自己從MD的目標中裡除去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.45,0:07:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別胡來，我會把你引爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的弱點是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機體的基本性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.82,0:07:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和人手控制的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.16,0:07:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連機動力和反應速度\N也完全一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題只是血肉之驅的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對那速度能否應付得來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.90,0:07:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我來說，宇宙機雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.80,0:07:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比MD之流更可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.07,0:07:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不需要MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.08,0:07:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部白色傢伙由我來收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.75,0:07:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現目標，先由MD進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.19,0:08:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙來宇宙有甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.44,0:08:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是MD吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的反應慢了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要轉為近身戰就有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有兩部嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.72,0:09:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵擋住了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對付這傢伙\N也要用近身戰嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.61,0:10:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們在和我的戰鬥中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙敢做這種事的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很少見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒時間陪你們玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.56,0:10:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點帶我走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.97,0:10:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你潛入了OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.47,0:10:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是特洛瓦‧巴頓特士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯‧馬吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.64,0:10:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該是初次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘了自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.92,0:10:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字是米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.32,0:10:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我作為從地球的親善大使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住在宇宙的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.34,0:11:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大半是技師和勞動人口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.61,0:11:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們忍耐著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.94,0:11:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比地球惡劣的環境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.01,0:11:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而他們想進步的那股幹勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.74,0:11:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,產生了新的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.61,0:11:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支援他們的財團就是溫拿家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫拿家的現任家主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.12,0:11:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,移居到自己的衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了確保衛星居民的權利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一直挺身而出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.43,0:11:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和地球圈統一聯合談判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在聯合軍崩潰了的現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也作為附近衛星的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.37,0:11:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以和平主義為前提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和OZ對抗到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫拿先生，來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.85,0:11:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說卡特爾回來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.92,0:11:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是多大時的照片呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.02,0:11:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，要妳專程送我來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，別客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有事要來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個不孝子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.04,0:12:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我還是認為自己是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.84,0:12:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類光是住在宇宙已經很不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼是戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.18,0:12:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無理兼無用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我們才一直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和地球圈統一聯合談判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.02,0:12:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以求解決問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.69,0:12:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不只乘坐機動戰士降落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還製造了攻擊衛星的藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.36,0:12:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果無人戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.36,0:12:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場戰爭就不會完結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，完結了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.37,0:12:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的戰爭完結了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能有何作為?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為小孩的你能有何作為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當一個繼承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要遵從父母的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再考慮清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是出色的繼承人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.82,0:12:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊莉亞，連妳也維護他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.32,0:13:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，小孩不一定毫無作為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.96,0:13:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我寶貴的弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.16,0:13:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個有志氣的繼承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.46,0:13:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸他其實也明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.63,0:13:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和OZ談判已經不能解決問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他認為所有衛星團結起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.74,0:13:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會仍然有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.08,0:13:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳為何不告訴我妳是我姐姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.95,0:13:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸曾告訴我弟弟\N是鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他很生氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.99,0:13:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽聞各位姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身在各地的資源衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.89,0:13:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家全部站在你那邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實爸爸也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.07,0:13:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一個人離家出走時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.37,0:13:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最擔心的是爸爸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.47,0:13:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的確是被聯合\N追趕才躲到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，根據溫拿家的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.52,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平根本不需要機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.48,0:14:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不理那思想單純地協助他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以武力解決問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又會產生新的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不明白那一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.71,0:14:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的鋼彈在這裡製成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我不小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓它在地球毀滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.76,0:14:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.56,0:14:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教授已經不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.39,0:14:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了戰鬥，我要再次製造鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.73,0:14:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在真的還能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.13,0:14:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了衛星的大家而戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.94,0:15:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你一樣戰鬥的\N鋼彈駕駛員被捉住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.41,0:15:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部鋼彈被當眾毀滅用來示警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.31,0:15:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而衛星的人看得好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.58,0:15:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.78,0:15:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經無人站在鋼彈那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.69,0:15:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾，你今後也能戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.32,0:15:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並非為了\N別人認同才戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家終有一日一定會明白我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去了沙漠鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我變得有點傷感呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.87,0:15:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，姐姐我只是說洩氣話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們大家都愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.55,0:15:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，不要悲傷\N我們的卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝妳，伊莉亞姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，你們所講的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.36,0:15:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將來的發展是甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何需要防衛軍備?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.70,0:16:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫拿大人\N我們也明白你的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.77,0:16:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這裡是危險的戰略據點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.37,0:16:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且市民想親手確保自身安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.78,0:16:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著這些擅自製造的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.08,0:16:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們聯想到\N和平安全等字眼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有溫拿氏你的財力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.39,0:16:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個衛星的開發就沒可能完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.43,0:16:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的繁榮是市民努力的成果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為今後不再須要獨裁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.23,0:16:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我何時獨裁過?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我反對OZ介入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全是為了衛星的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這裡真的有獨裁者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.91,0:16:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫拿大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.49,0:16:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來已經不可以由個人擁有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.02,0:16:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你快點決定\N交出這裡的管轄權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.09,0:17:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了製造武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.73,0:17:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了製造殺人工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為何要協助他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.65,0:17:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們在說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.75,0:17:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反對的聲音在增強啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.22,0:17:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們在喊不要獨佔資源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.89,0:17:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫拿家的確擁有很多資源衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.12,0:17:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們從未獨佔過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.66,0:17:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了人們在宇宙的繁榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們豁出一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家應該知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.57,0:17:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人的心改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的周圍是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.04,0:17:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸的周圍也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.14,0:17:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們…\N我們只是在做正確的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.35,0:18:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表決結果，全體一致通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這個資源衛星交由OZ管轄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不準他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這個衛星用來製造武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.15,0:18:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?\N爸爸把衛星切離了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.95,0:18:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!它在繼續加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.39,0:18:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.45,0:18:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許會影響到衛星的機能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是他的本性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.79,0:18:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只為了自己的利益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抹殺衛星的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最終做出這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.76,0:18:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以表決了嗎?各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.34,0:18:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然全體無異議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.47,0:18:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保衛衛星的和平與秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.51,0:18:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們馬上採取迅速的措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.09,0:19:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸!請你停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.22,0:19:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣做毫無作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追兵馬上就會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.36,0:19:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，妳叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.73,0:19:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對OZ的侵略袖手旁觀嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.37,0:19:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要再\N駕駛機動戰士戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.37,0:19:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武力不能解決問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.77,0:19:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!別來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.92,0:19:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那支討厭的雷射砲\N瞄準著這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.62,0:19:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親大人!請你快逃走!
