Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.08,0:20:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他絕對不是在逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他勇敢地戰鬥呢
