Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.13,0:20:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷勢會惡化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.33,0:20:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾你好仁慈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.80,0:21:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸也好仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.67,0:21:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.74,0:21:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種爸爸為何一定要死呢…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒人明白…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仁慈的人的眼淚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.05,0:21:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣，衛星滿意了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.89,0:21:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們滿意了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.06,0:21:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不會忘記…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.43,0:21:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且…\N絕對不會讓你們忘記啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.23,0:21:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日的事…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.04,0:22:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.44,0:22:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好寧靜啊
